: #222222; font-size: 9pt">(</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">低</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">) 25000</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">元</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">/</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">平方米</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">(</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">均</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">) 50000</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">元</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">/</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">平方米</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">(</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">高</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">)<br />\r\n	</span><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">项目介绍：绿地沃尔玛广场坐落于浦江镇普锦路江园路交界，紧邻浦江镇行政中心，占世博版图。为绿地集团与沃尔玛两大商业巨头联手打造，总建筑面积约</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt">4.5</span><font face="宋体"><span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial">万平方米的一座集购物、餐饮、休闲、娱乐为一体的大型综合商业广场。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style="text-justify: inter-ideograph; text-align: justify">\r\n	<span style="color: #222222; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial; mso-bidi-font-family: arial"><font face="宋体">来源：搜房网，所有文字图片等资料，版权均属搜房网所有，文章内容仅供参考，不构成投资建议，也不代表搜房赞同其观点。</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: arial; color: #222222; font-size: 9pt"><br />\r\n	&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US"><o:p><font color="#000000" size="3">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n', 24, '2012-03-23', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1);
