font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">土建工程师（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、男性，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">30</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁以上；</span><span style="font-size: 9pt"> <span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上房地产行业同岗位工作经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、吃苦耐劳，具有高度责任心。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">招商员（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、年龄在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">27</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁以上，商业管理、市场营销等专业本科及以上学历；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、熟悉商业地产业态，商业项目招商架构设计及过程控制，具备商业招商管理经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具备良好的心理素质，掌握商务谈判的技巧，以及客情维护能力；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具有家居建材资源且有招商项目的成功案例者优先考虑。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">一经录用，您将获得：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、业内较高水平的薪酬待遇；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、享受五险、节假日补贴、工作餐、年休假、各类津贴、年度体检等优厚福利；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、有机会接受专业的房地产知识培训，接触商业地产开发到经营全过程；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、集团公司提供的职业生涯长期发展平台及内部晋升通道。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">联系人：<st1:personname productid="刘" w:st="on">刘</st1:personname>小姐</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 0662-6888099<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>18666268117 <o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">附文信息：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">贵宾联线：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">0662- 689 9999<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">投资商：华科国际控股集团有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">开发商：阳江市华科市场投资有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">建筑规划：北京市建筑设计研究院深圳院</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">形象支持：深圳容纳广告</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font color="#000000">项目地址：广东省阳江市广雅路和华科南路交汇处</font></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n', 21, '2011-09-01', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `maxtron_notice` (`id`, `title`, `icon`, `content`, `cate_id`, `datetime`, `top`, `digest`, `state`, `sort`, `view`) VALUES
(107, '华科国际 十大核心价值 百年财富基石', '/uploads/images/%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%9F%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87/201109090.jpg', '<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">十大核心价值，百年财富基石</span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><img alt="" height="801" src="/uploads/images/多期报纸文字图片/201109090.jpg" width="550" /></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 无论是内地还是沿海，一个个以事实为证的例子告诉我们：哪里有大市场，那里就有取之不竭的财富、商机、宝藏！当下，家居建材产业作为&ldquo;国家支柱型产业&rdquo;之一，其商铺相比其他类型商铺更具投资价值。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">华科国际家居生活广场汇集十大核心价值于一体，必将成就其粤西南区域行业的领军地位和造就无数隐形富翁！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">市场升级，趋势价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">承接珠三角，家居建材市场迎来转型，一跃成为行业商贸核心，奠定项目家</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">居建材超级铺王地位。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">区位优势，绝对价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">粤西南之&ldquo;心&rdquo;，粤西南物流枢纽，粤西南商贸物流核心腹地。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">地段优势，决定价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">扼守滨海新城核心地段，五大城际交通干线汇聚，人流、财流围合，成就绝</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">对中枢，汇聚八方财富。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">规模优势，实现价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>50</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万㎡超级巨无霸体量，坐拥阳江，辐射粤西南，面向全华南。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">规划优势，发展价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">超前</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">20</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年规划，筑就世纪商业典范之作。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">政策优势，保障价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">市重点项目，政府、协会倾力打造。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">行业优势，整合价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">联合各大家居建材行业协会和商会，整合资源、共铸商业辉煌。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">推广优势，强化价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">亿巨资推广，经营促销每一天，消费者真正得实益，大市场、大平台、</span><span style="font-size: 9pt"> <span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">大生意、大财富，绝对强势做旺。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">品牌优势，提升价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">国际顶尖家居建材连锁企业强势加盟，并汇聚国内外近千个一线品牌，成就</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">粤西南行业巨擎。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">经营优势，延伸价值：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">自持</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">成物业，国际顶尖经营团队专业管理，共赢朝阳产业第一金。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">华科纳贤榜</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">诚邀业界精英加盟</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">共创美好未来</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">招商总监</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">35</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁以上，大专以上学历，营销、商业管理等相关专业毕业优先考虑；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具备</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上的招商公司或大型房企招商工作经验，有</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上同等职位工作经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、独立操作过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万㎡以上商业项目的招商工作，有大型专业市场特别是家居建材市场招商工作经验的优先考虑；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、熟悉商业地产经营管理流程，具有较强的商业推广渠道和招商策划能力；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具备出色的沟通能力、谈判技巧，富有责任心。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">工程部经理（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、男性，年龄</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">32</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">周岁以上，大专以上学历，工民建或建筑类专业；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上大型房地产公司同岗位工作经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、本专业高级技术职称；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具有高度的责任心并熟悉房产公司工程管理的各项流程。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">水电安装工程师（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、男性，大专及以上学历，电气工程相关专业；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上建筑电气设计或施工现场管理工作经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、熟悉强、弱电技术规范和相关施工工序；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、熟悉机电、市政工程验收工作流程。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">置业顾问（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、女，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">22-28</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁，大专以上学历，身高</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1.60</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">以上，五官端正，形象气质极佳，有较好的亲和力；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、懂基本商务礼仪，具备出色的表达、沟通能力，口齿伶俐，思维敏捷；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具备良好的心理素质，勇于面对压力和挑战，有志于从事房地产销售事业；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、勤奋敬业、为人热情积极，有较强的客户服务意识及团队合作意识；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、特别优秀者可放宽条件限制。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">土建工程师（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、男性，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">30</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁以上；</span><span style="font-size: 9pt"> <span lang="EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年以上房地产行业同岗位工作经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、吃苦耐劳，具有高度责任心。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">招商员（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">名）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、年龄在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">27</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">岁以上，商业管理、市场营销等专业本科及以上学历；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、熟悉商业地产业态，商业项目招商架构设计及过程控制，具备商业招商管理经验；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具备良好的心理素质，掌握商务谈判的技巧，以及客情维护能力；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、具有家居建材资源且有招商项目的成功案例者优先考虑。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">一经录用，您将获得：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、业内较高水平的薪酬待遇；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、享受五险、节假日补贴、工作餐、年休假、各类津贴、年度体检等优厚福利；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、有机会接受专业的房地产知识培训，接触商业地产开发到经营全过程；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">4</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">、集团公司提供的职业生涯长期发展平台及内部晋升通道。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">联系人：<st1:personname productid="刘" w:st="on">刘</st1:personname>小姐</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"> 0662-6888099<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>18666268117 <o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">贵宾联线：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">0662- 689 9999<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">投资商：华科国际控股集团有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">开发商：阳江市华科市场投资有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">建筑规划：北京市建筑设计研究院深圳院</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">形象支持：深圳容纳广告</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">项目地址：广东省阳江市广雅路与华科南路交汇处</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n', 21, '2011-09-09', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1);
INSERT INTO `maxtron_notice` (`id`, `title`, `icon`, `content`, `cate_id`, `datetime`, `top`, `digest`, `state`, `sort`, `view`) VALUES
(108, '华科国际 视点聚焦：访华科集团董事长林乃科先生', '/uploads/images/%E5%A4%9A%E6%9C%9F%E6%8A%A5%E7%BA%B8%E6%96%87%E5%AD%97%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87/201109230.jpg', '<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">巨擘启航</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-size: 12pt"> </span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">&ldquo;市&rdquo;无前例</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">&mdash;&mdash;视点聚焦：访华科集团董事长<st1:personname productid="林乃科" w:st="on">林乃科</st1:personname>先生</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;<img alt="" height="801" src="/uploads/images/多期报纸文字图片/201109230.jpg" width="551" /></font></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">&ldquo;中国最具幸福感城市&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国优秀旅游城市&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国刀剪之都&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国最佳生态城市&rdquo;、&ldquo;中国温泉之乡&rdquo;等美誉，对阳江而言，数不胜举。阳江作为最具发展潜力城市和三次产业协调发展的新型工业化城市，被誉为粤西南的&ldquo;经济快马&rdquo;，经济结构得到完美的优化，极大刺激了阳江经济，促进了阳江房地产行业飞速发展。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">地产开发就是家居建材的命脉！当阳江城市&ldquo;东联&rdquo;运动风起云涌，当保利十里银滩、碧桂园、龙熙山、半山四季、御墅龙山等一个个高品质社区拔地而起，当品牌消费日益形成潮流，阳江家居建材市场面临大升级，华科国际家居生活广场应势而生！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">那么华科国际家居生活广场是一个怎样的项目，它的出现又将对阳江家居建材市场的发展起到怎样的促进作用呢？带着这些疑问，我们专程拜访了华科集团董事长<st1:personname productid="林乃科" w:st="on">林乃科</st1:personname>先生。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">记者</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：林董您好，华科国际家居生活广场（以下简称：华科国际）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">日开工典礼的盛况在阳江引起了巨大轰动，市民们对于这个阳江历史上规模空前的商业项目充满了好奇和期待，今天我们就是带着大家关心的问题来访问林董，请您为大家答疑解惑。首先，请问贵公司为什么选择在阳江开发项目呢？</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">林董</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：谢谢大家对华科国际的关注！谈到在什么样的城市开发项目这个问题，我需要介绍一下我们集团自身的情况。作为一个专业的商业地产开发运营商，华科国际控股集团经过</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">15</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年的发展，已成为一个跨行业、跨区域的大型集团，业务范围涉及商业地产投资开发、现代物流业投资、商业经营管理及国际进出口贸易等领域。商业地产作为集团的核心经营业务，开发范围包括城市综合体、专业市场、购物中心、星级酒店、商业步行街区、旅游地产等多种类型。公司已成功开发了江苏泰兴国际装饰城、台州新明国际家居生活广场、舟山科来华红星美凯龙家居生活广场、舟山船用商品交易市场、平湖中国服装城、合肥用世生活城、江苏宿迁水韵城等多个大型专业市场。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">选择阳江，就因为我们看好这个城市！凭借多年的经验和市场考察标准，我们发现阳江具有很大的潜力。阳江作为粤西南地区的&ldquo;经济快马&rdquo;，去年人均</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">GDP</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">较</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2005</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年翻了一番，以此增速发展，预计到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2020</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年，人均</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">GDP</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">将增至</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">12</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万元。阳江今年住宅开发量近</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">200</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万㎡，按每年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">℅的增速和以</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">1000</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">元</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">/</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">㎡的家居建材需求估算，未来</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">10</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年将蕴含</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">320</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">亿元的市场需求。地理位置上来看，阳江地处泛珠三角，处于广州、珠海、佛山、江门、茂名、湛江的中心位置，均在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">小时车程之内，拥有海、陆、空立体交通网络，阳江的经济发展潜力可见一斑。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">我可以自信地说，阳江华科国际的出现占据了天时、地利和人和等有利条件。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">记者</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：听完您的介绍，加深了我们对阳江的了解，也对阳江的未来更有了信心。刚才提到阳江华科国际的出现占据了天时、地利和人和等有利条件，您能不能给我们详细介绍一下？</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">林董</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：通过阳江经济的发展背景，可以看出阳江的房地产业及家居建材市场拥有巨大的潜力，然而却缺乏一个与房地产行业发展相配套的家居建材专业市场。阳江家居建材市场面临升级，《阳江统计报告》中曾明确提到&ldquo;建立专业家居建材市场，搭建家居建材专业市场品牌的宣传平台&rdquo;。顺应市场需求，我们开发了华科国际，项目得到各级政府的高度重视，被评为&ldquo;阳江市重点项目&rdquo;。这一点是项目的&ldquo;天时&rdquo;。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">项目地处阳江</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">6300</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万㎡滨海新城核心，城市主干道广雅路和政府规划的华科南路、华科北路在此相汇，四面环街，广东省重点中学、国家级示范性普通高中&mdash;&mdash;广雅中学距项目咫尺之遥。项目</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">5</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">～</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">15</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">分钟车程内，西部沿海高速、沈海高速、云阳高速、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">325</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">国道和建设中的广东沿海高铁，五大城际主干线汇聚围合，交通条件得天独厚。项目总规划建筑面积约</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">50</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万㎡，设有美食餐饮街、市场配餐中心、五星级商务楼等服务配套。这些是项目的&ldquo;地利&rdquo;。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">做旺一个大市场，必然要整合第三方资源。感谢各级政府和社会各界一直以来对我们的关注和支持。项目作为阳江市重点项目、阳东县招商引资重点项目，阳东县委、县政府主要领导曾现场办公，宣传、工商、税务等各部门配合支持项目开发建设，制订各项优惠措施和扶持政策来保障项目长期稳定发展和繁荣。同时，我们还联合中国家居建材装饰协会、广东省浙江温州商会等几十家协会、商会，共同谋划项目辉煌未来。这些就是项目的&ldquo;人和&rdquo;。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">前面提到的华科国际开工典礼，中央、全国人大及省市的各级领导、全国各大家居建材行业协会及商会代表、国内外知名家居建材品牌商家和厂家代表等纷纷应邀出席。我们得到了政府、协会的鼎力支持，政企共同联手，致力于打造粤西南一站式家居建材交易平台。华科国际的出现，将结束阳江家居建材行业缺乏配套专业市场的历史，它不仅仅是一个大市场，在满足家居建材消费的同时，更可以为顾客提供包含餐饮、休闲娱乐等在内的一站式服务。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">记者</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：正如您所说，阳江的房地产业发展潜力巨大，然而却缺乏与之配套的家居建材专业市场，因为之前粤西南地区市场上没有出现如此大规模的家居建材专业市场，现在大家比较关心能不能真正地做大做旺，您能不能向我们介绍一下这方面的情况？</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><font size="3">林董</font></span></b><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">：一个成功的市场离不开前期的科学规划，华科国际规划有&ldquo;商品交易中心、国际会展中心、仓储物流中心、电子商务中心、金融服务中心、商务配套中心、多功能服务中心等&rdquo;十大中心，不仅要将项目打造成为粤西南家居建材专业市场，更要奉献一个国际化专业样板市场。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">为了将项目做大做旺，我们推出&ldquo;统一定位、统一规划、统一招商、统一推广、统一经营、统一管理&rdquo;等六大统一经营举措，以及&ldquo;建立国际专业经营管理团队，建立国际化电子商务平台，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">亿巨资推广，每年举办阳江家居博览会、定期举行行业峰会论坛，联合开发商共创促销计划&mdash;&mdash;入伙礼券、抽奖永不停，开通全城小区免费交通巴士，创办市场周报、特刊及免费发放采购黄页，政务一条龙服务，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">30</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">天无理由退货，建立装潢设计免费咨询中心&rdquo;等十大保障性运营政策，更自持项目</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">成物业，就是决心与广大入驻商家共同繁荣市场，共同赢取海量财富。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">拥有</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">300</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">多万平米专业商业地产开发经验和千亿市场需求做铺垫，我对项目的未来充满信心。同时，我相信，华科国际的出现，会对阳江以及整个粤西南地区的家居建材市场升级整合起到巨大的推动作用，促进阳江向&ldquo;家居建材商贸之都&rdquo;迈进，我们愿意与入驻商家，与</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">400</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">万阳江人民共赢未来！</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><font color="#000000"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">另外，记者了解到，汇聚众多资源优势的华科国际家居生活广场，自</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">8</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt">6</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">日开工以来，外地客、商络绎不绝奔涌而来，考察、咨询项目情况，事实证明：华科国际顺应市场需求，得到了广大客户和商家的认可。</span></font><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 21, '2011-09-23', 0, 0, 1, 0, 1),
(109, '华科国际 热烈祝贺2011年阳江市建筑装饰协会年会暨华科国际家居生活广场项目说明会 圆满成功', '', '<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">热烈祝贺</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt">2011</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年阳江市建筑装饰协会年会</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">暨华科国际家居生活广场项目说明会</span></b><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">圆满成功</span></b></font></p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align="center" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">主办单位：阳江市建筑装饰协会</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">协办单位：华科集团</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><st1:chsdate day="28" islunardate="False" isrocdate="False" month="9" w:st="on" year="2012">9<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><span lang="EN-US">月</span></span>28<span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial"><span lang="EN-US">日</span></span></st1:chsdate><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">，</span>2011</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">年阳江市建筑装饰协会年会暨华科国际家居生活广场项目说明会在广博园半山酒店盛大召开。协会领导、各会员单位负责人、行业人士纷纷应邀参加，会议除了对阳江市建筑装饰协会进行工作总结和展望之外，还重点对华科国际家居生活广场进行了推介说明和讨论，嘉宾纷纷表示：华科国际家居生活广场选择在行业黄金发展时期出现，正迎合了市场发展的需求，同时以其强大的规模、高档次的定位和超前的规划不仅可以满足阳江的需求，更将催化整个粤西南的家居建材消费，市场前景显而易见。华科国际家居生活广场的出现标志着阳江结束了无综合统一家居建材专业市场的局面。会议上，华科集团董事长林乃科先生向协会各会员单位及行业人士详细介绍了华科国际家居生活广场的市场定位、规划优势、经营策略等项目情况。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p><font color="#000000">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">以下为阳江建筑装饰协会部分会员：</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江装饰在线</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">北京东易日盛装饰公司阳江分公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市佳信装饰设计工程有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市江城区星艺装饰设计中心</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳春市集美装饰有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">圣保罗地板粤西总经销</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市金陶建材有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">香港皇朝家私</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市福晖贸易有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市源星五金交电有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市华科市场投资有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳春饰意居装饰公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市春申投资置业有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市东篱装饰设计有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市乾晖装饰设计有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市江城区皮阿诺橱柜商店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">菲林格尔地板阳江专卖店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">立邦漆阳江专卖店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市创新艺术玻璃厂</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">太太乐厨电</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">好太太厨电</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">花雕装饰</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市广通恒冷技术服务有限公司</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">圆方园家具</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市江城区名匠装饰设计</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">图腾室内装饰设计</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳东县东城镇康家地板经营店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">阳江市江城区金福象原木门</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">天虹电线厂（江城区海诚线缆经营部）</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">冠湘原木楼梯扶手</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">诗尼曼整体衣柜阳江专卖店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">江城区皇家窗帘装饰布艺店</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">\r\n	<font color="#000000"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 9pt; mso-ascii-font-family: arial; mso-hansi-font-family: arial">江城区视界家饰装饰材料经营部</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 9pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=